                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18451124-17-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18451124-17-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18451124-17-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 handkerchief, the goods of <persName id="t18451124-name-161" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18451124-name-161" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
